    dc:description "FIGURES 15 – 17. Trichromothrips fragilis n. sp. (female): (15) Head & pronotum; (16) Antennal segments I – VIII (right); (17) Mesonotum & metascutum (sculpture line on mesonotum omitted.). Scale bar = 0.04 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/170413/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.170414>
    dc:description "FIGURES 18 – 21. Trichromothrips fragilis n. sp. Abdominal segments. Female 18 – 19: (18) Tergum II (left side); (19) Terga VIII – X (sculpture lines on tergum VIII omitted); male 20 – 21: (20) Tergum IX; (21) Sternum VII. Scale bar = 0.04 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/170414/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

